OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFord to cut one in five    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fjobs in the UK             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ford has announced plans to cut 1,300  
OL,6, jobs in the UK over the next two years,
OL,7, a fifth of its total workforce in the  
OL,8, country.                               
OL,10,FIt is part of a major restructuring    
OL,11,Fprogramme that will see the carmaker   
OL,12,Fcut 3,800 jobs overall across Europe.  
OL,14,FFord is cutting back on development    
OL,15,Fstaff as it faces an uncertain economic
OL,16,Ffuture and prepares for the transition 
OL,17,Fto electric vehicles.                  
OL,19,FMost of the UK cuts will be at its     
OL,20,Fresearch site at Dunton in Essex.      
